==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Extensor
<hw>Ex*ten"sor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., one who
stretches. See <er>Extend</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>A muscle
which serves to extend or straighten any part of the body, as an arm or
a finger; -- opposed to <contr>flexor</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Extensure</ent>⟦br⟧
